        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_NAME" Language="zh_Hant_HK"><Text>崩壞能感知</Text></Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_DESC" Language="zh_Hant_HK"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩壞能研究點[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]一切的開始。</Text></Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KEY_OF_FINALITY_NAME" Language="zh_Hant_HK"><Text>終焉之鑰</Text></Row>
        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_KEY_OF_FINALITY_DESC" Language="zh_Hant_HK"><Text>消耗 {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] 崩壞能研究點[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]最終權限。</Text></Row>

