        <Row Tag="LOC_HONKAI_TECH_PERCEPTION_DESC" Language="en_US"><Text>Cost {1_Amount} [ICON_HONKAI_RESEARCH] Honkai Research[NEWLINE][NEWLINE]The beginning.</Text></Row>
